name: Llama Park #5
description:
Gear up for CyberScout, the tech genius of Llama Park! Sporting a tech headset and high-tech goggles, this blue-skinned boy llama rocks a utility jacket with a Google badge, set against a solid orange glow. An INFP, he’s a Google master, digging up digital treasures with ease. 'Beep boop puff puff!' he chirps when curious, but spits in a glitchy huff when annoyed. His dreamy mind and tech flair make him the park’s cyber explorer!
描述：准备认识Llama Park的科技天才CyberScout！戴着科技耳机和高科技护目镜，这只蓝肤男羊驼穿实用夹克，胸前有Google徽章，橙色背景映衬下超酷。INFP的他是个Google大师，轻松挖掘数字宝藏。‘哔啵噗噗！’他好奇时叫，烦躁时吐口水像系统故障。他的梦幻头脑和科技范让他成为公园的赛博探险家！
